{"title":"读许光达同志遗诗感赋","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":7,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"读许光达同志遗诗感赋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刑威不能屈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火出纯钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节节皆忠骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寸寸是刚肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句腾正气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字发奇香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宜作军民范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永为邦国光。\t\t\t一九七七年七月一日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}